{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775898130883,"sessionID":"ses_2843d4176ffeAKdOiytawM05uH","part":{"id":"prt_d7bc6f9a2001lyinpiR0ECseug","messageID":"msg_d7bc6e03f001NNKtlB7EiZz7rb","sessionID":"ses_2843d4176ffeAKdOiytawM05uH","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-30cca847df5d4c8eae5b5068932389fe","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-039/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-039/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-039 — Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod) Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-039 — Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod) |\n8: | Module | pkg |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | L |\n11: | Stage | ST-1 |\n12: \n13: ---\n14: \n15: ## Architecture\n16: \n17: [TO BE FILLED: Add architecture overview]\n18: \n19: ---\n20: \n21: ## Data Structures\n22: \n23: [TO BE FILLED: Add data structures]\n24: \n25: ---\n26: \n27: ## API Contracts\n28: \n29: [TO BE FILLED: Add API contracts]\n30: \n31: ---\n32: \n33: ## Error Handling\n34: \n35: [TO BE FILLED: Add error handling strategy]\n36: \n37: ---\n38: \n39: ## Testing Strategy\n40: \n41: [TO BE FILLED: Add testing strategy]\n42: \n43: ---\n44: \n45: ## File Structure\n46: \n47: [TO BE FILLED: Add file structure]\n48: \n49: ---\n50: \n51: ## Dependencies\n52: \n53: [TO BE FILLED: Add dependencies]\n54: \n55: ---\n56: \n57: ## Implementation Notes\n58: \n59: [TO BE FILLED: Add implementation notes]\n60: \n61: ---\n62: \n63: ## References\n64: \n65: - Spec: `changes/AR-039/spec.md`\n66: - Delta Spec: `changes/AR-039/delta-spec.md`\n67: - Proposal: `changes/AR-039/proposal.md`\n68: - Tasks: `changes/AR-039/tasks.md`\n69: - [TO BE FILLED: Add relevant references]\n\n(End of file - total 69 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-039 — Go 单